@startuml
title SaxonForms component model and one-hop environment interactions
skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam packageStyle rectangle

package "Browser Environment" {
  [HTML/DOM Tree] as DOM
  [DOM Event Loop] as EVENT_LOOP
  [JavaScript Runtime\n(xforms-javascript-library.xsl)] as JS_RUNTIME
}

package "SaxonForms Runtime" {
  [XForms Source\n(xforms:xform / xhtml:html)] as XFORMS_SOURCE
  [SEF Transform\n(saxon-xforms.sef.xml)] as SEF
  [Model State\n(instances, binds, MIPs)] as MODEL_STATE
  [Action Dispatcher\napplyActions\noutermost-action-handler\n(src/saxon-xforms.xsl)] as ACTIONS
  [Submission Adapter\nHTTPsubmit\nxforms-submit\n(src/saxon-xforms.xsl)] as SUBMISSION
  [Function Library\nxforms-function-library.xsl\nxforms-xpath-functions.xsl] as FUNC_LIB
  [XSD Helpers\nxsd-helpers.xsl] as XSD
}

package "SaxonJS 3" {
  [Interactive XSLT Engine\nixsl:* extension functions] as SAXONJS
}

XFORMS_SOURCE --> SAXONJS : "SaxonJS.transform2({stylesheetLocation})"
SAXONJS --> SEF : execute xformsjs-main
SEF --> MODEL_STATE : xforms-model-construct
SEF --> FUNC_LIB : xforms:impose(), xforms:instance()
FUNC_LIB --> MODEL_STATE : evaluate-xpath-with-context-node
MODEL_STATE --> XSD : xsdh:is-type-valid()
MODEL_STATE --> DOM : xforms-refresh\nrefreshOutputs-JS
DOM --> EVENT_LOOP : native onchange/onclick/onkeyup
EVENT_LOOP --> ACTIONS : ixsl:onchange/onclick mode templates
ACTIONS --> SEF : action-* named templates
SUBMISSION --> JS_RUNTIME : ixsl:promise (fetch)
SUBMISSION --> MODEL_STATE : instance replacement/merge
JS_RUNTIME --> EVENT_LOOP : promise callback
JS_RUNTIME --> DOM : readFileAsXML(), setFocus()

note right of ACTIONS
One-hop browser interactions are explicit:
DOM and JS runtime are first-class neighbors.
Symbol names map to templates in saxon-xforms.xsl.
end note
@enduml
